        {
            "title": "城堡證券：散戶情緒轉淡 歷史規律暗示美股短線有望反彈",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 城堡證券策略師表示，散戶投資者情緒轉淡，可能預示著美國股市短期內有望反彈。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">城堡證券股票及股票衍生品策略主管Scott Rubner表示，根據該公司平台數據，上周個人交易者轉為美國股票和期權的淨賣家。傳統上，散戶一直是股市中最看漲的群體之一。自2020年1月以來，這種情況僅出現過18次。此前數周，伊朗戰爭和油價飆升引發股市劇烈波動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Rubner在周二致客戶的報告中寫道：「我們現在看到，散戶在現貨和期權市場都開始出現初步的投降跡象，散戶參與已不再是單向的需求來源。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a88ac255-f832-3fc7-a560-36dfb2902eee-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這種看空轉向明顯背離了近年來散戶持續逢低買入的行為模式。但城堡證券數據顯示，從歷史上看，散戶出現疲態的時期往往伴隨著美股更強的短期回報：在類似信號出現後的兩個月裡，標普500指數約有82%的概率上漲，平均漲幅為4.1%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管散戶上個月仍是淨買家，但參與度大幅放緩。3月淨名義支出較前一個月下降約55%，較1月峰值下滑約70%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一放緩出現在資產價格經歷劇烈波動之後。中東衝突升級擾亂能源市場，標普500指數3月下跌約5%。布倫特原油今年以來已上漲約80%，進一步加劇通膨擔憂，並拖累風險資產表現。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Citadel Securities Sees Retail Exodus Setting Stage for S&amp;P Run</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9F%8E%E5%A0%A1%E8%AD%89%E5%88%B8-%E6%95%A3%E6%88%B6%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92%E8%BD%89%E6%B7%A1-%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E8%A6%8F%E5%BE%8B%E6%9A%97%E7%A4%BA%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E7%9F%AD%E7%B7%9A%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%88-163907898.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-08 01:14:04",
